<script lang="ts">let{data,form}=$props();</script><svelte:head><title>导航分类｜暮色工作台</title></svelte:head><header class="studio-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">NAV CATEGORIES</p><h1>导航分类</h1><p>可以随时新增分类；删除前需要先清空分类中的网站。</p></div><a class="primary" href="/studio/sites">返回导航收藏</a></header>{#if form?.message}<div class:success={form.success} class="notice">{form.message}</div>{/if}<div class="manager-grid"><section class="studio-panel manage-list">{#each data.categories as c}<article><i class="color-dot" style={`background:${c.color}`}></i><div><b>{c.name}</b><small>{c.siteCount||0} 个网站 · 网址标识：{c.slug} · 排序 {c.sortOrder}</small><span>{c.description}</span></div><form method="POST" action="?/delete" onsubmit={(e)=>!confirm('确定删除这个空分类？')&&e.preventDefault()}><input type="hidden" name="id" value={c.id}/><button class="danger" disabled={Boolean(c.siteCount)||data.categories.length<=1} title={c.siteCount?'请先移动或删除分类中的网站':data.categories.length<=1?'至少保留一个分类':'删除分类'}>删除</button></form></article>{/each}</section><section class="studio-panel editor"><p class="eyebrow">NEW</p><h2>新增导航分类</h2><form method="POST" action="?/save" class="studio-form"><label>分类名称<input name="name" required /></label><label>分类网址标识 <small>用于内部链接，留空自动生成</small><input name="slug" placeholder="例如：design-tools" /></label><label>分类介绍<textarea name="description" rows="4"></textarea></label><div class="two"><label>颜色<input name="color" type="color" value="#6857d9" /></label><label>排序<input name="sortOrder" type="number" value="100" /></label></div><button class="primary">新增分类</button></form></section></div>
